    {
      "name": "request_kaicalls_update",
      "title": "Request KaiCalls Update",
      "description": "Ask the KaiCalls on-behalf update broker to perform a scoped, governed mutation. Supported intents: phone.emergency_address.set, transcripts.sink.configure, agent.patch. Mutating requests need an idempotency_key; high-risk changes need human authority. The broker returns needs_user_input, needs_approval, pending_approval, executed, denied, or unsupported — never an unaudited side effect.",
